name: Cheesey Mousey
description:
If you find a hard time running the game in your browser, try another browser (recommend chrome) or please download the windows version!

This is a hardcore platformer with interesting color switching mechanics!

This is actually my first Jam and I really looking forward for feedbacks!

I hope you can ENJOY!

Tips: if you find yourself stuck, feel free to press F12 to SKIP LEVELS!
